quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  12,101,My Dominus Vos dedit me kingship taught me interpretation de dreams Initiator de caelum terra; Vos est my Dominus Magister in hoc vita Hereafter Let me abiit prout submitter comes me cum the righteous
